{
  "body": "A [user had trouble understanding](http://colabti.org/irclogger/irclogger_log/perl6?date=2018-07-30#l831) the section [on interpolation in regexes](https://docs.perl6.org/syntax/%20Regex%20Interpolation).\r\n\r\nI glanced at it, and it's a giant codeblock that shows a lot of irrelevant stuff, like `.flip` inside `$(...)` coercer. The `<{...}>` form also looks out of place and probably belongs in the section about blocks.\r\n\r\nIMO that section could use a bit of cleanup and organization.",
